                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "34588235-8b32-48d4-8461-0701dbf6f6ac",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "The ship-by date is Friday 2026-04-17 per the signed PO. Leger's spring window resets Monday the 20th — miss the window and the full order gets rejected. The order is $18K, roughly 35% of Q2 forecast, and Leger is our first real department-store channel. A clean first fulfillment unlocks reorder conversations. A missed one kills the relationship with their buyer, who has already flagged us as \"unproven.\""
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
