                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "8d884957-ffe0-497d-8aab-d0fd10cd3b93",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "### 3. Mitigation Steps — T+60 to T+120"
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "6dcf84ec-72d3-49dc-8315-829282ed31f9",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "- If cause = our deploy: rollback to 2026-04-12-1830 via `./scripts/rollback.sh brew-pay 2026-04-12-1830`. Verify pod rotation completes."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "198996bd-3c08-4893-a2a8-bd5f630de652",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "- If cause = Stripe-side: flip `processor_fallback` flag to `adyen`. Run one synthetic transaction through Adyen sandbox first — do not fail over blind."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "dbc9a619-eae8-4aca-a37c-5787c8e2efe9",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "- If cause = DB pool exhaustion: restart brew-pay pods one at a time with 30-second gaps. Do not mass-restart."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "952e1820-295c-4b8c-9284-78de59ab5216",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "- After any fix: run synthetic checkout from test account `ops+canary@brew.io`. Require 3 consecutive successes before declaring the mitigation stable."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "42c31c55-4801-4af9-8d26-c4bf8aefd044",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "- Roll `payment_v3_rollout` back to production in stages: 10% → 25% → 50% → 100%, 5 minutes between steps. Abort on any error-rate spike above 2%."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
